data.description: 2BR/2BA single-level home with covered decks on front and back with beautiful views and close to town! New well, sprawling 17.44 acres and three shops! One finished 32x55, wired, loft, wood stove & insulated with amazing electric doors. One 33x56 with electric doors, wired & perfect for RV storage. One 30x50 machine shop with five bays. A small heated work shop and a tool storage shed. Cherry, apple, peach & pear fruit trees and plenty of room for garden and animals. Private road and serenity.
